description.en-us: Color Reveal is a sub-series of the Color Shifters series. The castings in this series are essentially Alternative versions of regular Color Shifters castings but are coated in a coat of water-soluble paint. When initially dipped in water and swirled around, the water-soluble paint coat of the casting dissolves; after the paint coat dissolves the casting acts like any regular Color Shifters casting. The paint coat application is often noted to be poorly done.
